Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_orcnt

MIX_ORCNT = MIX O-Ring Packets Sent Counter

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_ORCNT register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_ORCNT register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
